# Phase II — Obsession with Architecture (Spring–Summer 2022)

---

## Writing Pattern

Documented pattern from correspondence:

- Writing ~4 hours per day
- Majority of energy invested in worldbuilding
- Expanding magic systems
- Government structures
- Cultural codes
- Political theology
- Power mechanics

This is no longer just YA fantasy.

It is constitutional design.

