## Structural Transformation

Original Keeper structure:

- Minimalist
- Short chapters (~2 pages)
- Intimate POV
- Emotional compression
- Sparse exposition

2022 direction:

- Dense world scaffolding
- Deep system explanation
- Codex-first approach
- Mythic expansion

Minimalism is no longer the guiding aesthetic.

Completeness is.

